Topic Modeling

#try different k
pa_lda_ = LDA(dtm, k=10, control=list(seed="123"))
pa_topics_ = tidy(pa_lda_, matrix="beta")
pa_top_terms_ = pa_topics_ %>%
  group_by(topic) %>%
  top_n(15, beta) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  arrange(topic, -beta)

pa_top_terms_ <- pa_top_terms_ %>%
  group_by(topic) %>%
  top_n(15, beta) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  arrange(topic, -beta)

pa_top_terms_ %>%
  mutate(term = reorder_within(term, beta, topic)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(term, beta, fill = factor(topic))) +
  theme(text = element_text(size=12)) +
  geom_col(show.legend = FALSE) +
  facet_wrap(~ topic, scales = "free") +
  coord_flip() +
  scale_x_reordered()
